{"tid":23293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"侵仔Twitter發炮 轟中國操控貨幣南海擴軍","createTime":"2016-12-05T00:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T09:00:08.000Z","uid":13663,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f4819e9f01db53b3fba03604a92b4e3d3dc23d2","tid":23293,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T00:34:37.000Z","msg":"美國總統當選人特朗普周日晚在Twitter連珠炮發，指控中國操控人民幣匯率，並在南海展示軍力。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在推文說：「中國將他們的貨幣貶值（令我們的公司難以競爭）、向我們輸往中國的產品徵收重稅、或在南中國海興建軍事設施前，有沒有先問我們？」<br />\n<br />\n暫未清楚特朗普為何發那些推文。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普日前與台灣蔡英文總統通電話，打破美國多年外交慣例，引起風波。令人懷疑他上場後，會否改變美國對華政策。"},{"pid":"d77c9c17ee4f4ddf0af9d3250632e2957a89a47e","tid":23293,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T00:35:48.000Z","msg":"Did China ask us if it was OK to devalue their currency (making it hard for our companies to compete), heavily tax our products going into..<br />\n<br />\ntheir country (the U.S. doesn't tax them) or to build a massive military complex in the middle of the South China Sea?  I don't think so!"},{"pid":"92466616957dd1d5851598f4894e457f2b0e9e69","tid":23293,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T00:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.infostormer.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/trump-pepe-frog2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.infostormer.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F09%2Ftrump-pepe-frog2.png&h=df24be31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32ac63ad807d26c65e752a6dc0dd31c33716fc60","tid":23293,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T00:49:54.000Z","msg":"Trump Make America Great Again 👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻"},{"pid":"0b0e9773aeeade4d147aa91c969b3b3754c030bb","tid":23293,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T00:58:42.000Z","msg":"選舉果陣好撐侵班大陸哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a42270f21634cf044830f7a8c22fffddd920d2","tid":23293,"uid":3